From sis3149@sis.port.ac.ukSun Sep  3 22:30:06 1995
Date: Fri, 21 Apr 1995 12:31:53 +0100 (BST)
From: Stephen McNamara <sis3149@sis.port.ac.uk>
To: Blitzlist <blitz-list@helsinki.fi>
Subject: Debugger BETA

There's always a mistake made with my releases - at least this one is out 
the way early :)

When trying to run the install script it tries to find the program MDL 
(Make Def Libs).  But I forgot to include this program in the beta 
archive.  Anyone who really wants to use the install script should thus 
compile the Makedelibs.bb2 source into C:MDL.


Thank you.  Thats all folks :)

Steve Mc.

