>     - My version of Blitz Basic2 is 1.7.  I have been trying to use the
>       examples/blitzmode/dbscrolling.bb2 example to understand how to do
>       map block scrolling.  I was disturbed to notice that when 
>       running this example on my Amiga 2000 or my brother's 1200 that 
>       blocks which scrolled into view tended to blink/flicker especially 
>       when the joystick was moved quickly to change directions.
> 
>       Not all blocks would blink.  Perhaps just a few.  They would continue
