> library. But now i have an idea.. 
> i want to playback an animation directly from disk so .... I 
> need a little more information   ;)

Theoretically the library can be cludged so that it takes the address of 
a delta frame of animation to unpack.  Thus the programmer could load the 
frames in a few at a time and then tell the unpacking routine where to 
unpack from.  This wouldn't be too hard, but I don't know how 
efficient/fast it would be.



Steve Mc.

