thing to do.  (Esp. with kickstart 3.x, as pen-sharing would 
REALLY be screwed up.)  However, if you still want information on 
restoring the palette prefs, e-mail me and I'll send you some source 
examples of reading palette prefs (and restoring them) for 2.x and 3.x.





