   The current prefs files are in Ram:ENV/ somewhere (possibly 
ENV:sys/pallete.prefs)  and are, from what I gather .iff files. 

   You may be able to get at the colours from the LoadPalette(*)  command as 
this uses that format.  Otherwise experiment with this file.  When not in 
the Env: drawer. They usually reside in sys:prefs/envarchive (guess name 
again) alough this may change. (On my system I have Env-Archive.1 
Env-Archive.2 and Env-Archive.3 for different setups). 
  
  I appologise if I sound like I am guessing and I am wrong, but I 
haven't seen my amiga for about 7 weeks and I forget things easily) 

yours -- Chris

