Do you mean to save an Newtype in a file or what? I also need help in
this subject!

It could be so easy just to write:

 ...
   resetlist(my)
   if openfile(0,"ram:test")
        fields 0,my.newtype
        while nextitem(my)
            put 0,i
            i+1
        wend
    closefile 0
 ...

[ no warranty, this is *crap* source!]

and now you must put each newtype-item in a variable and put this 
variable in the record... Or is there another way to do it??

