>  Does anybody know how to get rid of the title bar from an intuition screen?
>   jay@burns.demon.co.uk

Sorry if this has been answered; think our mailer's been acting up.

Anyway, use the intuition call ShowTitle.

I don't have my books nearby, but I imagine it should be something like:

ShowTitle_(Addr Screen SCRN, BOOL)

Where SCRN is the number of the screen object and BOOL is a boolean value
(i.e. TRUE=-1/FALSE=0).

The call takes the address of the screen structure and the boolean.

Christopher Jennings
EBA


