Vaughan,

> B.T.W. Is it possible to add a bar item (i.e. ~~~~~~) to my menus?

What I do is just this:

    Menuitem 0,0,0,1,"item 1"
    Menuitem 0,0,0,2,"------"
    Menuitem 0,0,0,3,"item 2"

And don't do anything in the case statement for the item hit
result.. okay so the line gets hightlighted but it does the trick
visually.

