Hi Vaughan, you wrote in <199504181837.EAA23453@yoyo.cc.monash.edu.au> on Apr 19:

> B.T.W. Is it possible to add a bar item (i.e. ~~~~~~) to my menus?

You have to set the flags in "MenuItem" to $40, and as Menutext you
put "String$("~",length)" . Eventually you have to fit it in the menu
using "MenuGap"

