From sis3149@sis.port.ac.ukSun Sep  3 22:30:10 1995
Date: Tue, 9 May 1995 09:27:44 +0100 (BST)
From: Stephen McNamara <sis3149@sis.port.ac.uk>
To: Blitzlist <blitz-list@helsinki.fi>
Subject: GadTools Menus

Well I was bored yesterday so I wrote a quick Gadtools menu library.  Its 
not fully working yet (still gotta add a GTSubItem command) but it does 
work in exactly the same was to the original menus lib.  Meaning that 
you can exchange all MenuTitle commands with GTMenuTitle without any 
syntax problems.

The bar separators are also available for you to use, and since its 
GadTools all the laying out is done beautifully :)


Later,
Steve Mc.

