From: MO Tiffany <cca93057@sun1.bham.ac.uk>
To: blitz-list@helsinki.fi
Subject: Re: What is ABC

> What the hell is This ABC thingy (apart from the obvious!).

Basically a repackaged new version of Blitz (was to be essentially the same
program as what you would get with BUM8 - but due to delays....).
New manual (ringbound).

> Also How do you use the Display copper effects such as DisplayRainbow
> as everytime i use them an not enough room error appears.

When you set up a display theres a parameter at the end - can`t remember
what its name was, but you need to set up copper space for it.  Its in the
BUM6/7 docs, or more easily in the BB2 guide (on the ftp site).

Mark Tiffany /SgtBilko

