developing Multi Media Software & Animations on the PC. I will go 
back to Blitz when the AmigaCard is ready but for now: greetings and 
maybe we meet again. You can still reach me for other conversations 
if you like.

Hereby is the Dutch Blitz User Group gone...

To ACID: change your way of support if you want to survive! I was good
enough when there where troubles here but afther that you let me 
down. Thanks (not).

My last point: Blitz changed my life, it was the most powerfull 
language I used in my Amiga years, I hope a PC version will come! 

CYa!



