I think we are getting a bit bogged down with this help thang.

<excuse the possible lack of spaces - this keyboards a bit dodgy>

I think the help lib should just have a small help text that can appear (ill
wait to see what Nigels got...), and possibly also have a link to an amigaguide
or HTML doc. using bookmarks (anyone know how to use those in amigagguide??).

Otherwise we would be reinventing the car, not jsut the wheel!!!

The markupstuff was really intended for the smallhelp text,so that you could
possibly put in the odd italic or bold char.  Yes -use the samecodes as html,
but only support a few.

