Well, a suggestion sometime ago for higher timing rates is actually already in
the FAQ (still only in HTML on my web page (see the sig)).  

This was to use the Vpos command to get the vcertical position of the beam,
which gives you 1/256 (or 1/200 i NTSC) of a vertical blank.

Dont know if this is fast enough...

Mark

