Nigel, Its me again.

I did however get this to work (but its slower???)

 p$="Myprog
 f$="NIL:"
 Execute_ &p$,&f$,0
 end
 
 This has an error because its wrong sytext. you dont need the () and `
 and you need an extra parameter (0) ?
 |
 |
Execute_ (&p$,&f$)`

See YA!



From sis3147@sis.port.ac.ukSun Sep  3 22:30:15 1995
